title: Trees Great Tastiness Dripeth Grape Jesus Thrice (Greatest Hits)
description:
This is a collection of songs released by Grape Jesus (Matt Thaden) Between June 2013 and June 1st 2014.

This is the third set of the collections entitled "Grapest Hits" 

The music is experimental, low-fi, minimal, improvisational music in terms of performing instruments. This matches and follows alongside a plethora of electronic music in the minimal genre as well as genres such as breakbeat, trap and D'n'B

Grape Jesus pertains to a non-commercial experience and all songs are available for free. 

Support Grape Jesus by spreading the word to friends, spreading the torrents such as these, and supporting the acceptance of music such as the minimal and improvisational styles Grape Jesus uses to approach the edge of music, and begin cutting away at the edge itself.

So they say of wisdom that it were but the three wise men that knew that a great child had been born in Nazareth.
